data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home is located in the highly desired gated community of Plantation Oaks.  The home features an eat in Kitchen and a spacious great room perfect for entertaining and family life. The Roof is only one year old.  The home has a large screened in porch (32X10).  The yard is fenced in for your privacy and has a sprinkler system.The community features a resort style pool and club house.The community also has boat and trailer storage area. Easy access to Kennedy Space Center, Blue Origin and Space X. The A/C is only 10 years old.  A must see!
